ragel|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
ragel: ragel (Finite state machine compiler)
ragel:
ragel: Ragel compiles finite state machines from regular languages into
ragel: executable C, C++, Objective-C, or D code. Ragel state machines can
ragel: not only recognize byte sequences as regular expression machines do,
ragel: but can also execute code at arbitrary points in the recognition of a
ragel: regular language. Code embedding is done using inline operators that
ragel: do not disrupt the regular language syntax.
ragel:
ragel: http://www.colm.net/open-source/ragel/
ragel: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
